      "id": "funnels-intro",
      "type": "text",
      "props": {
        "text": "<h1><span style=\"color: #ffc000; font-size: 48px; font-weight: 800\">A funnel is not just a page. It is a guided sales system.</span></h1>\n        <p><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400\">Most businesses lose leads because visitors are given too many choices, no clear next step, and no automatic follow-up after they leave. A funnel fixes that by focusing every page, form, message, offer and automation around one conversion goal.</span></p>\n        <p><span style=\"color: #e6eef5; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400\">With Gr8 Result Digital Solutions, a funnel can connect your landing pages, lead magnets, forms, calendar bookings, quotes, email marketing, SMS follow-ups, CRM pipelines, phone activity and reporting into one connected journey. The result is simple: more enquiries captured, faster follow-up, better sales conversations, and fewer opportunities slipping through the cracks.</span></p>",
        "textSize": "medium",
        "alignment": "center",
        "minHeight": "90px",
        "textColor": "#e6eef5",
        "fontFamily": "system-ui",
        "fontWeight": "400",
