    {
      "id": "funnels-map",
      "type": "text",
      "props": {
        "text": "<h2><span style=\"color: #ffc000; font-size: 46px; font-weight: 800\">The Gr8 Result Funnel Map</span></h2>\n        <p><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400\">A strong funnel is not a random collection of pages. It is a connected path where every action triggers the next useful step.</span></p>\n        <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,minmax(0,1fr));gap:18px;margin:34px auto 0;max-width:1280px;text-align:left;\">\n          <div style=\"background:#0b1220;border:1px solid rgba(56,189,248,.45);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;\"><strong style=\"color:#38bdf8;font-size:22px;\">1. Attract</strong><p style=\"color:#dbeafe;font-size:18px;line-height:1.6;\">Ads, social posts, organic content, referrals and email traffic land on a focused campaign page.</p></div>\n          <div style=\"background:#0b1220;border:1px solid rgba(255,192,0,.45);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;\"><strong style=\"color:#ffc000;font-size:22px;\">2. Capture</strong><p style=\"color:#dbeafe;font-size:18px;line-height:1.6;\">Forms, offers, bookings and quote requests collect the details needed to continue the conversation.</p></div>\n          <div style=\"background:#0b1220;border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,.45);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;\"><strong style=\"color:#22c55e;font-size:22px;\">3. Nurture</strong><p style=\"color:#dbeafe;font-size:18px;line-height:1.6;\">Email, SMS, task reminders and call prompts keep the lead moving while interest is highest.</p></div>\n          <div style=\"background:#0b1220;border:1px solid rgba(236,72,153,.45);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;\"><strong style=\"color:#ec4899;font-size:22px;\">4. Convert</strong><p style=\"color:#dbeafe;font-size:18px;line-height:1.6;\">The CRM tracks the opportunity through booking, quote, proposal, sale, review and repeat business.</p></div>\n        </div>",
        "textSize": "medium",
        "alignment": "center",
        "minHeight": "90px",
        "textColor": "#e6eef5",
        "fontFamily": "system-ui",
        "fontWeight": "400",
        "hideBorder": true,
        "lineHeight": 1.45,
        "paddingTop": 80,
        "paddingBottom": 80,
        "textAnimation": "fade-up",
        "enableParallax": false,
        "textLineHeight": 1.45,
        "backgroundColor": "#121c26",
        "baseLayoutWidth": 1500,
        "fullWidthBackground": true
      }
